OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mostly cloudy with some
OL,6,Fpatchy light rain, this mainly across
OL,7,FMoray and northern Aberdeenshire. Best
OL,8,Fchance of some brightness across
OL,9,FDeeside and southern Aberdeenshire.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FChance of a few outbreaks of
OL,12,Frain across northeastern Aberdeenshire
OL,13,Fthis evening. Otherwise it will be a
OL,14,Fdry night with variable amounts of
OL,15,Fcloud and clear periods.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FIt will be a dry day with
OL,18,Fvariable amounts of cloud and sunny
OL,19,Fspells, best of the sunshine later on.
OL,20,FVery warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
